  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this survey is to investigate the current state of sepsis care around&#xD;
      Europe. The study is aiming at hospital structure, emergency departments, wards, intensive&#xD;
      care units and clinical diagnostic and microbiological service.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
